### Python Club

We are a group of scientists working at the Institute of Astrophysics in Pontificia Universidad Catolica de Chile. We will be hosting a Python Club during the second term of 2016. We are planning to meet on Wednesday at 5 pm every two weeks in *Sala se Seminarios* at the *Instituto de Astrof√≠sica* in Campus San Joaquin. You are welcome to join us.
